# --- graphify knowledge graph ---
# Track the curated graph (graph.json, manifest.json, GRAPH_REPORT.md,
# cost.json, .graphify_labels.json). Ignore the heavy query cache, the dated
# auto-backups (git history is the real backup), and machine-local markers.
graphify-out/cache/
graphify-out/20*-*-*/
graphify-out/.graphify_python
graphify-out/.graphify_root

